      "content": "It’s just that everything feels so... passive. Like I'm just waiting for the clock to run out, waiting for some accident or some sickness to finally do what I can't do myself. It feels so undignified, just sitting here decaying, waiting for a random moment to end it. I wish I didn't feel so helpless about the whole thing.",
